* sodium azide (dangerous): with a cyanide source like HCN or TMSCN enables tetrazole synthesis. Also, HCN + ethylene oxide → 3-hydroxypropionitrile.
* isopropyl source like propylene or isopropanol for making isobutyric acid (oxidation), diisopropylamine, DIPEA.
